com.broadcom.bt.le.api
Class BleAttribute

java.lang.Object
  com.broadcom.bt.le.api.BleAttribute
Direct Known Subclasses:
BleCharacteristic, BleDescriptor
public class BleAttribute
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a Bluetooth LE attribute. BleCharacteristic and BleDescriptor objects are derived from this class.
